      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "高校生の誕生日と言えば、まずは沢山遊びます！\nということで、ゲームセンターにやって来ましたー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When it comes to high school birthdays‚ first you gotta have tons of fun!\nSo‚ we’ve come to the arcade~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、制服でこんな所入っていいの……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ are we allowed to be here in our uniforms…?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、今日はおかたいことは言いっこなしやで\n高校生にもなればみんな来てるもんやし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui‚ no stuffy talk today‚ okay?\nHigh schoolers come here all the time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.870417931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.604898103
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなのね……でも……\n補導とかされたらアイドル活動が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see… but…\nWhat if we get caught by a hall monitor? It’ll affect our idol activities…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5715647697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.104898103
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、そんな怯えんでも大丈夫やって\nスタッフさんもおるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ you don’t have to be so scared.\nThe staff is here‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9166.666666700003,
          "startTime": 43
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.8388664245
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "それより、普通の高校生は誕生日記念に友達と\nぱしゃプリ撮るみたいやで～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ normal high schoolers take Purikura\npictures to commemorate their birthdays.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.4007178433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.8209297815
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.5042033753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ちょっと……！　行っちゃった\nぱしゃプリってなんなのかしら……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ hold on…! They’re gone…\nWhat is Purikura…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.5542631148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.6209297815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "あのブースの中で撮影して遊ぶんだよ\n撮った写真がちっちゃいシールになって出てくるの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You take pictures and decorate them in that booth.\nThe pictures you take come out as small stickers!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.1542631148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.8875964481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "写真ならスマホで撮れるじゃない？\n何か違うの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it’s just photos‚ can’t you take them with your smartphone?\nWhat’s the difference?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.6209297815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.3209297815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "全然違うよー！　瑠依ちゃんも撮ってみたら\nぱしゃプリが病みつきになっちゃうかもよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's totally different~! Once you try it‚ Rui-chan‚\nyou might get hooked on Purikura!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6875964481,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2979.0702186000003,
          "startTime": 70.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、撮影の設定出来たで～\nはよ中に入って撮ろ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re all set for the shoot~.\nLet’s hurry up and get in there~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.399995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.7667307853
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "ぱしゃプリ……やられたわ……こういう遊びだったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Purikura… You got me… So this is what it is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.8000603039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.2667269706
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "楽しんでくれて良かった！　瑠依ちゃんが\n追加でお金を入れた時はびっくりしたよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad you're enjoying it!\nI was surprised when you put in more money~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7865947224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.5333936373
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "せやなぁ、すっかりハマってもうて、悩んだあげく\n「トリエル参上」って書くとは思わんかったわ。ぷぷっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ you got totally into it‚ and after thinking about it for a while‚\nI never thought you’d write “TRINITYAiLE has arrived”. Pfft.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.2666625977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.3148225147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなに笑わなくてもいいじゃない！\nそれに、すみれだって似たような落書きだったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t have to laugh that much!\nAnd besides‚ Sumire‚ you did similar doodles‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.3481596628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.1814891814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ、そう？　トリエルとは書いたけど、私のは\n「トリエル最強！　瑠依ちゃんハピバ」だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Really? I did write TRINITYAiLE‚ but mine\nsays “TRINITYAiLE is the strongest! Happy birthday‚ Rui-chan!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.2481596628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.0148225147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ二人とも似たもん同士ってことやな～\n星見プロのみんなにも見せてあげましょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you’re both birds of a feather~.\nLet’s show it to everyone at Hoshimi Pro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.5214892386
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "もうっ、恥ずかしいから絶対やめてね。それで……\n結局このシールはどこに貼るものなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ that's embarrassing‚ don't you dare! So…\nWhere are we supposed to put these stickers?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7548263866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.1881559053
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "学校のみんなは、いつも使うペンケースとか\nノートとかメモ帳に貼ってたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The kids at school used to put them\non their pencil cases‚ notebooks‚ and memo pads.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.5214930533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.1881559053
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、事務所の冷蔵庫に貼って\nトリエルの仲良しアピールしてもええねんで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui‚ you could put it on the fridge at the office\nto show how close TRINITYAiLE is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.1666625977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.4722593623
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_51_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに私物に貼るわよ。すみれの言う通り\n毎日使うものがいいのかも。なんだか勇気がわくし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm obviously going to put it on my own stuff. Like Sumire said‚\nIt’d be better to put it on stuff I use every day. It makes me feel encouraged…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.972263177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
